title="Managing Heterogeneous Medical Data: Learning from Experiences in Telemedicine",
booktitle="VII Latin American Congress on Biomedical Engineering CLAIB 2016, Bucaramanga, Santander, Colombia, October 26th -28th, 2016",
year="2017",
publisher="Springer Singapore",
