abstract="Application of ICT (Information and Communications Technology) is turning into reality which collects health and exercise-related information in real time without constraint on space, facilitating constant heath management and prevention of geriatric diseases. Exercise-related mobile healthcare platform has attracted attention. In order to ensure constant prevention and management of geriatric diseases, smart exercise management system applicable to exercise prescription is needed which collects data related to exercise prescription such as type, intensity, frequency of exercise, and monitors biological information that changes during exercise. Constant prevention and management of geriatric diseases, smart exercise management system applicable to exercise prescription is needed which collects data related to exercise prescription such as type, intensity, frequency of exercise, and monitors biological information that changes during exercise. Individuals' health-related information and biological information data, stored via wearable devices and smartphone, have great value as big data in healthcare sector and are expected to be fully leveraged as next-generation health management method that offer advantages such as greater convenience and low cost.",
