abstract="This paper proposes architecture for a multi-user system for reminding medication, especially aimed at older people since they are those who have more difficulty managing their medication. Throughout the paper the proposed system and its key functionalities are described. Furthermore, the main research questions associated with the projected system are enumerated; and a research plan which will allow those issues to be addressed and which will evaluate the feasibility of the idea is also presented. Finally the methodology which is intended to be put into practice is indicated and how the research results can be obtained is also defined.",
