abstract="This paper presents a medical distributed system whose main goal is to enable real-time triage processing and further propagation of the data and patient history. The system uses various biosensors and mobile devices, as well as additional communication equipment. The system aims to ease the decision of priority in treatment, as well as to further monitor and alarm state change.",
