and Kim, Jeong Tai
and Park, Mignon
and Kim, Jongbae
and Lee, Heyoung
and Khalil, Ismail",
title="Requirements for the Deployment of Sensor Based Recognition Systems for Ambient Assistive Living",
booktitle="Aging Friendly Technology for Health and Independence",
year="2010",
publisher="Springer Berlin Heidelberg",
